{"tid":266264,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"HDMI cable + 轉插","createTime":"2017-06-01T10:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T18:58:33.000Z","uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1d2de5f974ba411a4f14af1fb1264ca1122bee","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"想搵條性價比高又要偏去高質，有冇介紹？<br />\n同埋因該電視得幾個洞，而家乜都用hdmi<br />\n有冇一開幾，但又可以保持質素？"},{"pid":"80f2ee5cede3152e1453038a3bff34aefc7fa57a","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836ae6e847aa76d3e7f3a0d372036d55ae47cdfc","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070031d020ed9cca280b45b7b272c87d493b1499","tid":266264,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"唔明你講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad96e6da954bdd44e3afb65850fb7edc82f70401","tid":266264,"uid":66395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明你講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係又要平又要勁<br />\n最好唔使錢"},{"pid":"44d217800b155f5a1d362cad7ccc44ea66d239e8","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔明你講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係又要平又要勁<br />\n最好唔使錢</blockquote><br />\n抵用囉"},{"pid":"4909651f82efc9cb8f2dd977392714953903013e","tid":266264,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"淘寶解決啦。<br />\n買條hdmi2.0線+個hdmi switch/ splitter。<br />\n兩樣加埋都唔過100。<br />\n<br />\nHdmi線貴同平差好少嫁咋，<br />\n行digital唔同行analog"},{"pid":"6f9265e5014639fff4b84b95e64cc4270a7f1cc6","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶解決啦。<br />\n買條hdmi2.0線+個hdmi switch/ splitter。<br />\n兩樣加埋都唔過100。<br />\n<br />\nHdmi線貴同平差好少嫁咋，<br />\n行digital唔同行analog</blockquote><br />\n但點解我用bluray player 駁電視睇bluray 都好唔清"},{"pid":"81f33917fb47e721301671c79bafa0f38901a1c0","tid":266264,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淘寶解決啦。<br />\n買條hdmi2.0線+個hdmi switch/ splitter。<br />\n兩樣加埋都唔過100。<br />\n<br />\nHdmi線貴同平差好少嫁咋，<br />\n行digital唔同行analog</blockquote><br />\n但點解我用bluray player 駁電視睇bluray 都好唔清</blockquote><br />\n其實有分別，試過香港80蚊廢線同淘仔HDMI 20蚊人仔，淘仔畫質有明顯改善，當然仲要睇係咪你電視問題"},{"pid":"62567a8778e7ee926a4c3866257c30fb50a7a3ee","tid":266264,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"用開Sony 線+aten hdmi switch, for 電腦同PS4 駁mon，效果ok, 畫面清，色水ok<br />\n<br />\n以前用過幾隻有牌子都易壞，d Sony 線用左5-6年，插notebook 成日蚊蚊插插都冇壞過"},{"pid":"e499393b7b008a49d93330bd81107f58ca97bea6","tid":266264,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淘寶解決啦。<br />\n買條hdmi2.0線+個hdmi switch/ splitter。<br />\n兩樣加埋都唔過100。<br />\n<br />\nHdmi線貴同平差好少嫁咋，<br />\n行digital唔同行analog</blockquote><br />\n但點解我用bluray player 駁電視睇bluray 都好唔清</blockquote><br />\n其實有分別，試過香港80蚊廢線同淘仔HDMI 20蚊人仔，淘仔畫質有明顯改善，當然仲要睇係咪你電視問題</blockquote><br />\n分別係有, 但唔大,<br />\n只要條HDMI線的質素唔係話好差, 基本上都好難分得出。<br />\n<br />\n香港果d廢線就真係唔好提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9307083d12b3733a944f44529c36300e982dd4e","tid":266264,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淘寶解決啦。<br />\n買條hdmi2.0線+個hdmi switch/ splitter。<br />\n兩樣加埋都唔過100。<br />\n<br />\nHdmi線貴同平差好少嫁咋，<br />\n行digital唔同行analog</blockquote><br />\n但點解我用bluray player 駁電視睇bluray 都好唔清</blockquote><br />\n可以有好多原因:<br />\n1) 條HDMI線有損壞<br />\n2) 個HDMI port有問題<br />\n3) 電視/ bluray player display setting問題"},{"pid":"9c4e19cd8d6c80d9a2d63bfacb3206c4a1678453","tid":266264,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:32:27.000Z","msg":"Hdmi 線質素應該影響佢耐用度同距離....差嘅會閃閃吓,甚至冇signal, 畫質上應該冇分別<br />\n<br />\n好嘅20m 都得(當初design條友plot 錯左, 要左2,3條貴野黎試, 好彩有條得)<br />\n但就算你買到條貴嘢都唔代表好,都係要試, 除非你指明買有牌子嘅線, 噤就會好貴"},{"pid":"8aa746c56b952f5e820a1b57aac92e51a2354e60","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hdmi 線質素應該影響佢耐用度同距離....差嘅會閃閃吓,甚至冇signal, 畫質上應該冇分別<br />\n<br />\n好嘅20m 都得(當初design條友plot 錯左, 要左2,3條貴野黎試, 好彩有條得)<br />\n但就算你買到條貴嘢都唔代表好,都係要試, 除非你指明買有牌子嘅線, 噤就會好貴</blockquote><br />\n我都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81ada981fb490a2d7ba09e57e1dc9ea01044adc","tid":266264,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用開Sony 線+aten hdmi switch, for 電腦同PS4 駁mon，效果ok, 畫面清，色水ok<br />\n<br />\n以前用過幾隻有牌子都易壞，d Sony 線用左5-6年，插notebook 成日蚊蚊插插都冇壞過</blockquote><br />\n幾錢到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b657a31d676fbc1627921bca2d61e6fb835b9b3c","tid":266264,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用開Sony 線+aten hdmi switch, for 電腦同PS4 駁mon，效果ok, 畫面清，色水ok<br />\n<br />\n以前用過幾隻有牌子都易壞，d Sony 線用左5-6年，插notebook 成日蚊蚊插插都冇壞過</blockquote><br />\n幾錢到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真, 直接上淘寶搞掂啦。<br />\n我係淘寶買過三個HDMI switch + 超過5條HDMI線 (0.3-3米不等),<br />\n全部都好滿意, 無出現過問題。<br />\n最重要嘅係夠抵用~"},{"pid":"98bf43d2c0fe811b651c57843b6b3ec81fbf65a9","tid":266264,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:58:33.000Z","msg":"淘寶綠聯"}]}